BEGIN
rule "purchase is 140 dollars"
when 
    $p : Purchase (total == 140) 
then 
    $p.setDiscount($p.getDiscount() + 0.03);
    System.out.println("is 140 discount: " + $p.getDiscount());
end

when

    $p.setDiscount($p.getDiscount() + 0.03);

    $p : Purchase (total == 901) 
then 
    $p.setDiscount($p.getDiscount() + 0.03);
    System.out.println("is 901 discount: " + $p.getDiscount());
end

    System.out.println("is 20093 discount: " + $p.getDiscount());
end
